OL,3,C'Not foreseeable' someone would enter
OL,4,Cculvert where Noah Donohoe's body found
OL,6,FIt was not "reasonably foreseeable"
OL,7,Fthat someone would access the entrance
OL,8,Fto a culvert in which Noah Donohoe's
OL,9,Fbody was found, a senior Stormont
OL,10,Fofficial has told an inquest.
OL,12,FJonathan McKee from the Department for
OL,13,FInfrastructure (DfI) said he had never
OL,14,Fencountered another death which had
OL,15,Foccurred in the same circumstances as
OL,16,Fthat of the Belfast schoolboy.
OL,26,@nD@LOUnD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
